Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)
1. What sets Code Hair Ladies Salon apart from other salons in Dubai?
At Code Hair Ladies Salon, we pride ourselves on offering a unique and personalized experience to each of our clients. Our salon boasts over fifteen years of international experience, and our dedicated team is trained to utilize the latest styling techniques while delivering bespoke services and creative trends. Customer satisfaction is our utmost priority, and we go above and beyond to ensure that every client leaves our salon feeling pampered and satisfied.

2. What services does Code Hair Ladies Salon offer?
We offer a comprehensive range of hair and nail services, including haircuts, hair coloring, hair treatments, manicures, pedicures, and nail art. Whether you're looking for a sleek new hairstyle or a bold nail design, our skilled technicians are here to help you achieve the perfect look.

3. How often should I visit the salon for hair and nail services?
The frequency of salon visits can vary depending on your individual needs and preferences. As a general guideline, we recommend scheduling a hair appointment every 4-6 weeks to maintain your hairstyle and a nail appointment every 2-3 weeks to keep your nails looking their best. Our technicians can provide personalized recommendations based on your hair and nail care routine.

4. Are the products used at Code Hair Ladies Salon safe for hair and nails?
Yes, at Code Hair Ladies Salon, we use only high-quality, professional-grade products that are safe for hair and nails. Our salon is equipped with premium products and tools to ensure long-lasting results and minimize damage to your hair and nails. Additionally, our technicians are trained to adhere to strict hygiene protocols to ensure a clean and sanitary environment during all services.

5. Can I request a specific stylist or technician for my appointment?
Yes, you are welcome to request a specific stylist or technician for your appointment at Code Hair Ladies Salon. We understand that building a rapport with your stylist or technician is important, and we will do our best to accommodate your request based on availability.
